# Admin Dashboard Features Implementation

Implement multiple features for the EcoPoints admin dashboard: fix bottle logs filtering/pagination, add rows-per-page selector, create new admin pages with hardcoded data, update sidebar navigation, and enhance quick actions.

## Proposed Changes

### Bottle Logs Improvements

#### [MODIFY] [page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/logs/bottles/page.js)
- Add working search/filter functionality with state management
- Implement functional pagination with page navigation
- Add rows-per-page dropdown (20, 50, 100, 150, 200) defaulting to 20
- Expand mock data to 100+ records for testing pagination
- Add filter dropdown with options: Machine, Bottle Type, Status, Date Range

---

### Sidebar Updates

#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/src/Components/Sidebar.jsx)
- Rename "All Users" → "Manage Users"
- Add "Settings" item with `Settings` icon pointing to `/admin/settings`

