### New Admin Pages

#### [NEW] [page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/users/page.js)
- Manage Users page with table of users (hardcoded data)
- User data: ID, Name, Email, Role, Status, Points, Join Date
- Search, filter, and pagination functionality
- Edit/Delete action buttons

#### [NEW] [page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/users/permissions/page.js)
- Permissions management with role-based access control
- Role cards: Admin, Moderator, User, Guest
- Permission toggles for each role

#### [NEW] [page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/logs/access/page.js)
- Admin access logs showing admin activity
- Data: Admin name, Action, Target, Timestamp, IP Address
- Search and filter functionality

#### [NEW] [page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/rewards/page.js)
- Rewards inventory management
- Reward items: ID, **Photo**, Name, Description, Points Cost, Stock, Status
- **Photo upload functionality** for reward images (displays in cards)
- Add/Edit/Delete functionality with image preview
- Stock level indicators

#### [NEW] [page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/settings/page.js)
- System settings page with sections:
  - General Settings (Site name, timezone, language)
  - Points Configuration (Points per bottle size)
  - Notification Settings
  - Security Settings

#### [NEW] [page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/profile/page.js)
- Admin profile management
- Profile info card with avatar, name, email, role
- Edit profile form
- Change password section
- Activity summary

